Installation instructions for all systems
=========================================

Requirements:
-------------

- Python v2.7 (earlier versions may work but not tested.)
  http://www.python.org/

- PyODE v1.2 (tested with ODE v0.13)
  http://pyode.sourceforge.net/

- iVisual v0.1.87
  https://pypi.python.org/pypi/IVisual/0.1.87

Installation:
-------------

The package uses the easysetup / setuptools, so you can install it by calling

  python setup.py install  (as root on Linux)
or 
  sudo python setup.py install (on Linux)

which installs the package on your system.


